cards.content: {"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"53921bc5-af00-4820-9b18-13725d34b66b","level":1},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Readme"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"750b3ba7-41af-48e0-ab5e-34c614768089"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"这是我的个人说明书，这里会记录我所知道的一切。这个说明书是我和这个世界的交流方式，写这个说明书也是一个梳理自己的过程。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"d342232a-3127-4a01-bf9d-0e95ed3cd8c8"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"我认为个人应该尽量多的把经验或思考都落实到文字上存档起来。人生短暂，总不应该花太多的时间在迷茫上，写作是个逻辑思考的过程，通过写成文档更能方便他人查阅。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"52aeb710-5b7e-4545-869b-2e9daa38cd01","level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个说明书为谁而写？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"2802d1c9-16f7-483a-8440-fed9f9db32b8"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个是为我自己而写，更是为了每一个想了解我的人写的。我喜欢通过文字去了解一个人，我也希望别人也能通过文字了解我。我更希望我通过记录这些，让我也更了解自己。"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"191d1c6c-2799-458a-988f-cd2bf07b8b69","level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"说明书里会记录些什么？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"e9601a5e-1357-4b2a-a36d-c2964076808a"}},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"f05b35c2-39c0-4072-8b9a-8bc04e0656e0"}},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"5c754931-1381-4097-8bc6-583ec403ce5c"},"content":[{"type":"card","attrs":{"cardId":"1186d249-ed1a-48c1-971d-786f62b5817a"}}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"a099a78a-9f7c-4810-a832-7d5114da508b"}},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"d1dcc805-ca47-42ca-b77e-9ce45de23485"}},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"d7d665ff-da99-45ec-b753-60f868fb41d3"}}]}
